<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#step_Funbox_5> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#requires> "wpscan tool available" .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#step_Funbox_5> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#requires> "rockyou.txt wordlist available at /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt" .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#step_Funbox_5> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#next_step> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#step_Funbox_6> .
