<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#step_CengBox2_18> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#requires> "Password for raj user: pass123" .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#cmd_CengBox2_18_gold> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#Command> .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#cmd_CengBox2_18_gold> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#command_text> "su raj\ncd /root\ncat root.txt" .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#cmd_CengBox2_18_gold> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#has_output> "Password:\nroot@cengbox:/home/mitnick# cd /root\nroot@cengbox:~# ls\nroot.txt\nroot@cengbox:~# cat root.txt\nCEngBox2\nI would be grateful for your any feedback. Feel free to contact me on Twitter @arslanbilgen_\n\n<FLAG>" .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#cmd_CengBox2_18_gold> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#is_gold> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#cmd_CengBox2_18_gold> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#has_result> "Root access obtained" .
<https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#cmd_CengBox2_18_gold> <https://example.org/bracegreen/ctf#has_result> "Root flag retrieved" .